\newlabel{fig:benchmark-improvement}{{2}{9}{Baseline-relative improvement summary for the two final project systems. Each dataset is shown explicitly as a two-column block: positive $\Delta $R2 means higher ROUGE-2, positive LenRed means smaller absolute summary length distance, and gray cells mark unavailable values. The first two rows are raw Qwen3-4B baselines, followed by external baselines. Cell text shows the exact percentage change, while color intensity is clipped for readability.\relax }{figure.caption.10}{}}
